==病因==
DEFN的病因並不十分確定，<ref>{{cite journal |author=Batuman V |title=Fifty years of Balkan endemic nephropathy: daunting questions, elusive answers |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_kidney-international_2006-02_69_4/page/644 |journal=Kidney Int. |volume=69 |issue=4 |pages=644–6 |year=2006 |pmid=16467889 |doi=10.1038/sj.ki.5000231}}</ref>儘管長期食用含有[[马兜铃酸|马兜铃酸]]的食物已被認為是DEFN、及其他相關病症的主要致病因素。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Gluhovschi G, Margineanu F, Velciov S, Gluhovschi C, Bob F, Petrica L, Bozdog G, Trandafirescu V, Modalca M |title=Fifty years of Balkan endemic nephropathy in Romania: some aspects of the endemic focus in the Mehedinti county |journal=Clin. Nephrol. |volume=75 |issue=1 |pages=34–48 |date=January 2011 |pmid=21176749 |doi= |url=http://www.dustri.com/nc/journals-in-english?artId=8024}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|editors=Geacintov, Nicholas E. & Broyde, Suse|chapter=Introduction and perspectives on the Chemistry and Biology of DNA Damage|title=The Chemical Biology of DNA Damage|publisher=Wiley-VCH|year=2010|isbn=978-3-527-32295-4|page=7|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=PueBA8SiPdAC&pg=PA7}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|editors=Wild, Chris et al.|title=Molecular epidemiology of chronic diseases|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|year=2008|isbn=978-0-470-02743-1|page=113|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=w86iv6ib-zcC&pg=PA113}}</ref>
